  "source": {
    "about": {
      "content": "A merged corpus of English-language biomedical text comprising three sub-corpora: (1) PubMed article abstracts from 2000–2025, (2) clinical trial result summaries from ClinicalTrials.gov, and (3) de-identified hospital discharge summaries from three partner institutions.",
      "purpose": "Pre-training and domain-adaptive fine-tuning of large language models for biomedical and clinical NLP tasks.",
      "scope": "English text only. Excludes full article bodies, figures, tables, and supplementary materials. Clinical notes are restricted to discharge summaries; progress notes and physician orders are excluded."
